medieval-spell-speach-black-hole2 = Foramen Nigrum...

medieval-store-spells-darkness-black-hole-beginner-name = Black hole
medieval-store-spells-darkness-black-hole-beginner-desc = A weak piece of compressed mana follows your mouse cursor. Costs 50 mana.

medieval-store-spells-darkness-black-hole-middle-name = Giant black hole
medieval-store-spells-darkness-black-hole-middle-desc = Significantly better than its predecessor in absorbing matter. Costs 50 mana.

