# Cursed Arrow

medieval-spell-speach-cursed-arrow = Sagitta Maledicta

medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-beginner-name = Cursed arrow
medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-beginner-desc = Fire a cursed projectile from your hands. Costs 15 mana.

medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-kunai-beginner-name = Cursed arrows
medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-kunai-beginner-desc = Fire up to two arrows from your hands to selected points. Costs 20 mana. Use the middle mouse button to select multiple targets.

medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-kunai-middle-name = Cursed projectiles
medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-kunai-middle-desc = Fire up to three arrows from your hands to selected points. Costs 30 mana. Use the middle mouse button to select multiple targets.

medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-kunai-senior-name = Cursed kunai
medieval-store-spells-darkness-cursed-arrow-kunai-senior-desc = Fire up to five arrows from your hands to selected points. Costs 40 mana. Use the middle mouse button to select multiple targets.

