medieval-store-spells-darkness-spawn-skelet-middle-desc = Summons a meat skeleton, aggressive to everyone, at your selected point. Costs 35 mana.

medieval-store-spells-darkness-spawn-skelet-senior-name = Summon warrior skeleton
medieval-store-spells-darkness-spawn-skelet-senior-desc = Summons a warrior skeleton, aggressive to everyone, at your selected point. Costs 50 mana.

